  "text": "Note that for our proposed channel model the outputs at the legitimate receiver and the eavesdropper are conditionally independent given the channel input. A class of discrete memoryless channel models with this property was studied in [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] and a single-letter capacity expression was characterized.",
